// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0166 — Mass File Rename (unsafe)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: ad690b26-d86a-5b2c-8378-992586754162

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
